    "id": "v6"
  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "v\xE0 qu\xE1 m\u1EA1nh so v\u1EDBi t\xF4i. Cho n\xEAn \xF4ng h\xE3y \u0111\u1EBFn nguy\u1EC1n r\u1EE7a ch\xFAng n\xF3. R\u1EA5t c\xF3 th\u1EC3 t\xF4i s\u1EBD chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng v\xE0 \u0111u\u1ED5i ch\xFAng ra kh\u1ECFi b\u1EDD c\xF5i. T\xF4i bi\u1EBFt n\u1EBFu \xF4ng ch\xFAc ph\u01B0\u1EDBc ai th\xEC ph\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\u1EBFn, n\u1EBFu \xF4ng nguy\u1EC1n r\u1EE7a ai th\xEC h\u1ECDa \u0111\u1EBFn cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xF3.\" "), mdx("h6", {
