    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "Con l\u1EEBa th\u1EA5y thi\xEAn s\u1EE9 l\u1EA7n n\u1EEFa, n\xF3 li\u1EC1n l\xE1ch qua m\u1ED9t b\xEAn v\xE1ch \xE9p ch\xE2n Ba-lam v\xE0o \u0111\xF3. Ba-lam \u0111\u1EADp n\xF3 l\u1EA7n n\u1EEFa. "), mdx("h6", {
