  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Ba-lam b\u1EA3o n\xF3, \"M\u1EA7y l\xE0m nh\u01B0 tao ngu l\u1EAFm! N\u1EBFu c\xF3 g\u01B0\u01A1m trong tay th\xEC tao \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EBFt m\u1EA7y ngay b\xE2y gi\u1EDD r\u1ED3i!\" "), mdx("h6", {
